\ Evo audio: play three MIDI notes, then read the battery and blink on low.
\ `note` converts a MIDI number to a frequency pair; `beep` plays (dur, flag).
evo
60 note  30 0 beep-wait      \ middle C, 300ms, blocking
64 note  30 0 beep-wait      \ E
67 note  50 0 beep-wait      \ G, 500ms

\ light the LED red if the battery register reads low
REG_BATTERY readReg  20 <
if  127 0 0 led  then
OFF end
